{"tid":2118493,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"晚吹各行業發展|社工,會計,Design法律,IT,Marketing|如要進修\\DSE放榜選咩科好?","createTime":"2020-07-21T13:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T11:33:13.000Z","uid":343020,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b751d0fcfe272cb9630e9a721beda9715bb7cf87","tid":2118493,"uid":343020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:20:39.000Z","msg":"<strong>[網友互動]晚吹各行業發展|社工,會計,Design法律,IT,Marketing|如要進修\\DSE放榜選咩科好?</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dm4X4i7YfJw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fdm4X4i7YfJw&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=8aacb7ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dm4X4i7YfJw</a><br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------<br />\n大家做唔同行業又有冇自己既心得分享?<br />\n<br />\n自問唔係專家，只係一些透過個人經驗不斷學習翻黎的心得和分享<br />\n<br />\n我既目標係希望盡量幫香港人可以搜集一些實用/含經濟效益/搵到食既資料<br />\n計劃黎緊主要會上載既片/資源題材包括<br />\n求職/轉工<br />\n職業發展<br />\n進修<br />\n其他實用野等等...稔到再整<br />\n<br />\n有咩問題/意見可以係到分享<br />\n<br />\n其他:<br />\n轉工攻略01:包裝自己可以sell既技能有咩?<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/O2_GcY9H6ZA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FO2_GcY9H6ZA&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=b4b4b55a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/O2_GcY9H6ZA</a><br />\n<br />\n第一日返新工要注意啲咩?5招助你快速攻心!俾上司同事好印象<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EKPxIUReASY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEKPxIUReASY&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=a762e7a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EKPxIUReASY</a>"},{"pid":"df2ff45a63eb5105c282804671f5e3d34ce4c2ae","tid":2118493,"uid":104804,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:24:57.000Z","msg":"算啦做youtuber搵唔到食"},{"pid":"d105c7dceecba55a85e6a6677bc90d84a5b49b3a","tid":2118493,"uid":123696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:25:11.000Z"